messages.message:
Hi Folks, in an effort to make debugging easier for the Customers, we are writing a guide around request flows for common operations: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1OFnm3Q9gKsR36U9Wmx14G5cnfHK8BdBheBO6UdBbJX4/edit#. We’ve started with the most basic ones right now, but we hope to expand it to all the applications.  Let <#CV2A23127|> know if you’d love to contribute to this document :slightly_smiling_face:

Once @Mohit’s amazing working will be in, this document will become an artifact, but until then, whatever we can do to make our Customer’s life simpler, we should.
